{"tid":952711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五十年不變","createTime":"2018-12-23T11:09:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T11:26:46.000Z","uid":79709,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a48c1f3c5ae5ce981f5f4b7a979dde9c3f338ab","tid":952711,"uid":79709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T11:09:54.000Z","msg":"以前細個讀書 讀到香港回歸 <br />\n一直都覺得件事好柒<br />\n香港經濟 發展各方面都領先大陸咁多 <br />\n一個700萬人既城市 勁過一個13億人口既國家<br />\n中國憑咩收番香港？  配咩？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近睇左 新加坡超越香港個post<br />\n終於明白 原來就係憑香港回歸後五十年不變<br />\n見到依家既 香港政府 <br />\n其實都幾肯定五十年之後 香港收撚硬皮 <br />\n變成一個衰過深圳 既二三線城市 <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n依家就開定個post做見證 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8543b08838a61f02a16c94e3ae5c501d98a144","tid":952711,"uid":68787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6ad58d2df2841a27a4e5147b58a3bb25578cf8b","tid":952711,"uid":79709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd8543b08838a61f02a16c94e3ae5c501d98a144","tid":952711,"uid":68787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T11:26:46.000Z","msg":"點解你會覺得佢地冇做好自己份工？<br />\n政府既發展方針咪就係五十年不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}